title: What's The Difference Between DZ And You? 6/10: Jan. 6th, #MAGAgang, TMNT, Britney Spears, Justin Bieber, COVID Testing

description:
In this edition of What's The Difference Between DZ And You?, Miles and super producer DJ Danl discuss the Jan 6th primetime extravaganza, #MAGAgang, a video game round-up, Britney Spears' wedding, Justin Bieber taking a break, and the U.S. ending mandatory testing for travellers!
